title: Prince Imrahil of Dol Amroth | Tolkien Explained
description:
He's a beloved character from The Lord of the Rings - and with good reason!  Today, we cover the life and travels of Prince Imrahil of Dol Amroth, showing why he is such a great character of Middle-earth!

John Rhys-Davies is returning to Moria - and Nerd of the Rings!  Join me on Oct 17 as we celebrate Durin's Day with Gimli himself: https://youtu.be/pFYTKnwRItA
